                            <comment id="14470663" author="daniel_sun" created="Wed, 5 Jan 2011 05:48:34 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;C:\Documents and Settings\daniel_sun&amp;gt;groovysh -v&lt;br/&gt;
Groovy Shell (1.8.0-beta-2, JVM: 1.6.0_16)&lt;br/&gt;
Type &apos;help&apos; or &apos;\h&apos; for help.&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p&gt;1.8.0-beta-2 works fine.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14470584" author="blackdrag" created="Wed, 5 Jan 2011 06:23:20 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;you tried the a = &quot;&quot; part too?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14470582" author="eniosp" created="Wed, 5 Jan 2011 10:26:15 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;you have to create any variable. a = 1, myName = &quot;Joe&quot;. anything&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14472200" author="jwagenleitner" created="Mon, 16 Jan 2012 18:30:39 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Same problem also occurs for me on Linux, so not a Windows specific issue (maybe the description should be updated to remove the Windows reference).  Looks some rework in &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/groovy/groovy-core/commit/4cb39a287949182f5b7156088c48092157b92abc#L0L236&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;commit 4cb39a2879491&lt;/a&gt; may have caused the issue.  &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Based on &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/groovy/groovy-core/commit/4cb39a287949182f5b7156088c48092157b92abc#L0L250&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;this old line&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;def source = (imports + [ &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;true&lt;/span&gt;&apos;&lt;/span&gt; ] + buffer).join(NEWLINE)&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;and &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/groovy/groovy-core/commit/4cb39a287949182f5b7156088c48092157b92abc#L0R135&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;this new line&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;def buff = imports + [ &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;true&lt;/span&gt;&apos;&lt;/span&gt; ] + current&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I think the correct variable to reference in the &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/groovy/groovy-core/commit/4cb39a287949182f5b7156088c48092157b92abc#L0R130&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;if (io.verbose)&lt;/a&gt; line is &lt;tt&gt;current&lt;/tt&gt; instead of &lt;tt&gt;buffer&lt;/tt&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ve submitted a pull request for this at &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/groovy/groovy-core/pull/15&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/groovy/groovy-core/pull/15&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
